###############################################################
# ADMIN REFERRAL MANAGEMENT APIS
###############################################################

### 1. Get All Users Who Used Referral Codes (Basic - Default Pagination)
GET {{baseUrl}}/admin/referrals/used-users
Cookie: accessToken={{adminToken}}

### 2. Get Referral Users with Pagination
GET {{baseUrl}}/admin/referrals/used-users?page=1&limit=20
Cookie: accessToken={{adminToken}}

### 3. Search Referral Users by Name/Email/Phone/Code
GET {{baseUrl}}/admin/referrals/used-users?search=john
Cookie: accessToken={{adminToken}}

### 4. Get Referral Users Sorted by Referral Used Date (Latest First)
GET {{baseUrl}}/admin/referrals/used-users?sortBy=referralUsedAt&sortOrder=desc
Cookie: accessToken={{adminToken}}

### 5. Get Referral Users Sorted by Name
GET {{baseUrl}}/admin/referrals/used-users?sortBy=name&sortOrder=asc
Cookie: accessToken={{adminToken}}

### 6. Filter Users with Active Subscriptions Only
GET {{baseUrl}}/admin/referrals/used-users?hasActiveSubscription=true
Cookie: accessToken={{adminToken}}

### 7. Filter Users without Active Subscriptions
GET {{baseUrl}}/admin/referrals/used-users?hasActiveSubscription=false
Cookie: accessToken={{adminToken}}

### 8. Combined - Search + Filter + Sort + Pagination
GET {{baseUrl}}/admin/referrals/used-users?page=1&limit=10&search=test&sortBy=referralUsedAt&sortOrder=desc&hasActiveSubscription=true
Cookie: accessToken={{adminToken}}

### 9. Get Detailed Referral Info for Specific User
# Replace {{userId}} with actual user ID
GET {{baseUrl}}/admin/referrals/user/{{userId}}
Cookie: accessToken={{adminToken}}

